DEPT. OF JOB & FAMILY SERVS.
v.
DELPHI AUTOMOTIVE SYS., L.L.C. 2017-0553 Supreme Court of Ohio. April 26, 2019

MEDIATION MATTER

The case has been returned to the regular docket under S.Ct.Prac.R. 19.01. The appellant in each case shall file a brief within 40 days, and the parties shall otherwise proceed in accordance with S.Ct.Prac.R. 16.02 through 16.07. As provided in S.Ct.Prac.R. 16.07, the court may dismiss these cases or take other action if the parties fail to timely file merit briefs.
